     H            Y.                                                      EMD050
      ** AM#R450**************************************************
      *    FIX TMMC INOICE NUMBER IN SALES FILE                  *
      *    LEC  2024/09/05                                       *
      ************************************************************
     FAB#PL07 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
      * ----------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      * INVOICE NUMBER
     I            DS
     I                                        1  16 INV#
     I                                        1   5 IVSUPP
     I                                        6   7 IVNUKE
     I                                        8  16 IVODRN
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  16 B1NBAN
     I                                        1   5 B1SUPP
      * System Time(6) + Date(8)
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDTTM
     I                                        1   40WTIME
     I                                        7  140WDATE
     I                                        7  100WYY
     I                                       11  120WMM
     I                                       13  140WDD
      *
     C           K#07      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           ##NONY
     C                     KFLD           ##NKOJ
     C                     KFLD           ##NOYY
      *
      **
     C                     TIME           WSDTTM
      *
     C                     Z-ADD3503      ##NONY  40
     C                     MOVE 'B'       ##NKOJ  1
     C                     Z-ADD2024      ##NOYY  40
     C                     MOVEL'1731B'   ##SUPP  5
      *
     C           K#07      CHAINAB#PL07              50
      *
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C           B1SUPP    IFNE ##SUPP
      *
     C                     MOVEL##SUPP    IVSUPP
     C                     MOVELB1NUKE    IVNUKE
     C                     MOVELB1ODR1    IVODRN
     C                     MOVELINV#      B1NBAN
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWDATE     B1KSHZ
     C                     Z-ADDWTIME     B1TIME
     C                     MOVEL'QPGMR'   B1KSNA
      *
     C                     UPDATAB#PL071
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           K#07      READEAB#PL07                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      **
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
